{"tid":2284332,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"8.31事件7個月當晚屯門堵路 工人被判80小時社會服務令","createTime":"2020-11-13T08:18:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T08:47:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"340f2536b23d508355742feff971fcfb1bc64011","tid":2284332,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:18:03.000Z","msg":"8.31太子站事件發生7個月當晚，有市民響應網上號召到屯門堵路，警方到場驅散時，拘捕一名跟車工人，工人承認幫手傳遞竹枝，協助其他不相識的人堵路。他早前承認在公眾地方造成阻礙罪，裁判官今指堵路阻街時間不長，判被告接受80小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n署理主任裁判官張潔宜判刑指，被告的感化官報告整體內容正面，考慮案情不是同類控罪中最嚴重，被告阻礙他人的時間亦不算很長，且被告反省後顯出深切悔意，遂按報告建議判罰80小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/2JJYKB6NOBAYZD3YPC5LV6KDVU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2F2JJYKB6NOBAYZD3YPC5LV6KDVU%2F&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=bedb7959\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2F2JJYKB6NOBAYZD3YPC5LV6KDVU%2F&h=947fa0e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/2JJYKB6NOBAYZD3YPC5LV6KDVU/</a>"},{"pid":"010dc7ccab7f82d8aea42f544ce13ad45967fa61","tid":2284332,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:19:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4d6cf3f8a546b693ef904fa76342e5532d79b0","tid":2284332,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418dfa813b41b7d1838bcc80c553a89e8d3a5cbb","tid":2284332,"uid":305767,"li